cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the security challenges of wireless IoT networks and proposes an active learning approach for intrusion detection. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves wireless networks, which suggests cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as the second likely category. The proposed approach involves machine learning, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the design of a successful intrusion detection system, which could also fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering).
